{"id":2499,"date":"2025-05-13T09:03:51","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T09:03:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/?p=2499"},"modified":"2025-05-13T09:42:43","modified_gmt":"2025-05-13T09:42:43","slug":"tuyen-dung-quan-ly-tai-chinh-ke-toan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/tuyen-dung-quan-ly-tai-chinh-ke-toan\/","title":{"rendered":"TUY\u1ec2N D\u1ee4NG: QU\u1ea2N L\u00dd T\u00c0I CH\u00cdNH &#8211; K\u1ebe TO\u00c1N"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Trung t\u00e2m H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec \u0110\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt Hoang d\u00e3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (WildAct Vietnam) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c phi l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015. S\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0 trao quy\u1ec1n cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n lo\u00e0i v\u00e0 sinh c\u1ea3nh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf khoa h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ed1n ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n N\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n Lo\u00e0i v\u00e0 Sinh c\u1ea3nh<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u2013 K\u1ebf to\u00e1n tham gia \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u2013 k\u1ebf to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh cho c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chung.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:100,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559740&quot;:271}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c: <\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">01 n\u0103m (c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng).<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:100,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559740&quot;:271}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: <\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">01 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:100,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559738&quot;:9}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c:<\/span><\/b> <span data-contrast=\"auto\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:100,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559738&quot;:15,&quot;335559740&quot;:247}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">H\u1ea1n n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n \u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec3n<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">: 08\/06\/2025.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:100,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559