n<h3 aria-level=\"1\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5:<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:540}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd k\u1ebf to\u00e1n \u2013 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"51\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">H\u1ea1ch to\u00e1n, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed5 s\u00e1ch k\u1ebf to\u00e1n, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb, b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh theo chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c k\u1ebf to\u00e1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VAS) v\u00e0 c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"51\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Theo d\u00f5i thu \u2013 chi, c\u00f4ng n\u1ee3, t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u1ea1m \u1ee9ng, ho\u00e0n \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd qu\u1ef9 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t\/t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"51\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n, ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb thanh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang quy tr\u00ecnh.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">L\u1eadp v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"52\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0110i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i vi\u00ean d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch n\u0103m, ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch theo t\u1eebng ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"52\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Tham gia x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 kinh ph\u00ed trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh vi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 xin t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, \u0111\u1ea3<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"52\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu chi ph\u00ed th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy\u1ec7t, \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 r\u1ee7i ro v\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"52\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho Ban Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">B\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"53\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 (th\u00e1ng, qu\u00fd, n\u0103m) theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u01a1 quan nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"53\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">L\u1eadp b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch g\u1eedi cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"53\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ki\u1ec3m to\u00e1n (ki\u1ec3m to\u00e1n n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m to\u00e1n nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3).<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"54\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf, b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, thu\u1ebf TNCN v\u00e0 c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u2013 k\u1ebf to\u00e1n.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"54\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00e1c ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan; \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh quy tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"54\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn v\u00e0 t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean trong t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c quy tr\u00ecnh, ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u2013 k\u1ebf to\u00e1n hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"55\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh cho Ban Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c trong c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"55\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng, c\u01a1 quan thu\u1ebf, b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m to\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1c.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"55\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn kh\u00e1c hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 quy tr\u00ecnh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u2013 k\u1ebf to\u00e1n th\u00f4ng qua t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 aria-level=\"1\"><\/h3>\n<h3 aria-level=\"1\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u:<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">L\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245417&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:820,&quot;335559737&quot;:540,&quot;335559738&quot;:16,&quot;469777462&quot;:[820],&quot;469777927&quot;:[0],&quot;469777928&quot;:[1]}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&