h nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c k\u1ebf to\u00e1n \u2013 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh; \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean t\u1eebng l\u00e0m trong c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c phi l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"8\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfng Anh (\u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong \u0111\u1ecdc hi\u1ec3u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, l\u1eadp b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf);<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"9\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khi c\u1ea7n;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"10\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m k\u1ebf to\u00e1n &#8211; thu\u1ebf (\u01b0u ti\u00ean Quickbook), Excel, Google Sheets v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1c;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"11\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">C\u00f3 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u1eadp ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, theo d\u00f5i d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n, l\u1eadp b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"12\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 quy tr\u00ecnh thu \u2013 chi, mua s\u1eafm, gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n v\u00e0 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb trong c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n phi l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"13\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn quy tr\u00ecnh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:12}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"29\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;134224900&quot;:false,&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:821,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"14\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u01afu ti\u00ean \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3m to\u00e1n, c\u01a1 q